{"tid":224774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇圖】啱啱搭巴士，隔離條女挨左落黎...","createTime":"2017-05-01T10:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T16:36:22.000Z","uid":113004,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa292dcc08013e912ad701675df403a6bda3242","tid":224774,"uid":113004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱搭巴士，一上車見無乜空位就迫住同人坐。<br />\n<br />\n本身無乜留意嘅，但原來我坐左係個睇落24歲左右嘅女隔離。佢髮色微啡，着白色淨色T加黑色外套，灰色裙褲再加個黑色包包，睇落都幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一上車個陣已經見佢個頭鐘下鐘下咁，睇黎好眼訓。點知個巴士司機咁識做，開頭架車fing下fing下咁，跟住條女就有幾下挨左落我到，一頭嘅長髮披散係我整隻左手上。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有時候架巴左chok得太勁佢會震醒坐翻直，但成程車都挨左幾次落黎搞到小弟心如鹿撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對唔住我係小毒毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果各位巴打係我，你會點做？ 唔通係避開佢索性唔坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween 如果係絲打勿相認，小弟多多得罪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efb99474edae009d95e520ed5091595049965b5","tid":224774,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:17:10.000Z","msg":"比我會避開你先"},{"pid":"f91c5908bcb4016db2de0427ffe151756d310a9b","tid":224774,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:18:30.000Z","msg":"人地報左警未？"},{"pid":"972791b7248447a09319d7a3921d2f73823e1e7e","tid":224774,"uid":113004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比我會避開你先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢挨落黎，避開嘅權力係我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9076bb7059f1c95bf496ba3a808b0701d460b7c8","tid":224774,"uid":113004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地報左警未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估佢幾enjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該唔會報警"},{"pid":"3752b303e71a799e8f72f2e5d3fd39232b4a72cf","tid":224774,"uid":1165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"諗起復活節返鄉下 長途車 隔壁肥妹20歲左右 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個半鐘啊"},{"pid":"0a1a862ca18c06e4e6a9cf35a7e883c58a754da0","tid":224774,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地報左警未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估佢幾enjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該唔會報警</blockquote><br />\nok 網絡公審"},{"pid":"db83971c8286fdd1fd07c56affffc58bfee709d4","tid":224774,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"淨係試過比小朋友挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d761187b51a6c6e2fc2bc187b40e8bf8d8782de9","tid":224774,"uid":113004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起復活節返鄉下 長途車 隔壁肥妹20歲左右 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個半鐘啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打無事啊麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae09add4e6282a1a14f552da28ebb4a082cb556","tid":224774,"uid":113004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係試過比小朋友挨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n某程度上黎講都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b40f494e4f524d54d07c95e9d1c5ead8481901","tid":224774,"uid":113004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地報左警未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估佢幾enjoy<img src=\"/asse